+# Feature Schema Compare (P104) Dashboard — README
+
+## Dashboard: `feature_schema_compare_p104.json`
+
+### Import
+
+Grafana → **Dashboards** → **Import** → upload `feature_schema_compare_p104.json`.
+
+Select your Prometheus datasource when prompted.
+
+### Panels
+
+| Panel | Metrics | Notes |
+|---|---|---|
+| Last success | `feature_schema_compare_last_success` | 1 = OK, 0 = failed |
+| Age seconds | `feature_schema_compare_age_seconds` | Staleness from `updated_ts_ms` |
+| delta_auc | `feature_schema_compare_delta_auc` | AUC(schema_b) − AUC(schema_a) |
+| delta_brier | `feature_schema_compare_delta_brier` | Brier(schema_b) − Brier(schema_a); **negative is good** |
+| AUC by schema | `feature_schema_compare_auc{schema=...}` | Compares validation AUC |
+| Noise share by schema | `feature_schema_compare_noise_share{schema=...}` | Stability proxy (regime/hour) |
+| New features count | `feature_schema_compare_new_features_n` | Features present in schema_b but not schema_a |
+| Top-new mean AUC drop | `feature_schema_compare_top_new_mean_auc_drop` | Mean perm-AUC-drop for top new features |
+
+### Alert file
+
+```
+orderflow_services/prometheus_alerts_feature_schema_compare_p104.yml
+```
+
+Add to `prometheus.yml` → `rule_files:` (if you do not use the bundle manifest):
+
+```yaml
+  - orderflow_services/prometheus_alerts_feature_schema_compare_p104.yml
+```
